------------------
Turn Signal Rear Scenario's

None - Both Solid on Brake
Left - Left Flashes & Right solid on brake
Right - Right flashes & Left solid on brake
Hazard - Both Flash & Both Solid on brake

------------------

Ignition Current

0.105 A (Signals) + 4 A (Line Lock) + 0.01 A (Holley) + 0.05 (Alternator) + 0.2 A (Starter Relay)

Relay Box

1. Starter - 15 Amps
2. Rad Fan - 12 Amps
3. High Beams - 4 Amps
4. N/C
5. Sw 12v - 15 Amps
6. Water Pump - 7 Amps
7. Horn - 12 Amps
8. N/C - 

125A 6 AWG Main